A simple flask hello world application 

Prerequisites:
	- Python
	- Flask

How to run the application

1. Standalone:
	- cd flask-app
        - python hello.py

2. In a Docker container
        
	#Go to the direcory with the application
	
	- cd flask-app 
	
	#build the image
        
	- docker build -t flask-app . #build the image
        
	#Run the application in a conatiner 
	
	- docker run -d -p 5000:5000 flask-app
